  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103730/extras/f09256a307f07c83489cc3075f126b53.poster.avif?t=1728991765\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103730/extras/f09256a307f07c83489cc3075f126b53.webm?t=1728991765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103730/extras/f09256a307f07c83489cc3075f126b53.mp4?t=1728991765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Experience the most exciting and immersive beat-em-up combat system ever – become a kickass ninja and slice some demons in style! Join a band of wisecracking warriors in a bloody adventure through the land of mythical monsters and mysterious machines.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Play solo or with friends:</strong> 4 player local and online co-op<br></li><li><strong>Experience immersive and intuitive controls, or use classic \"button mashing\" technique:</strong> right analog stick controls your weapon giving you instant access to extensive moveset. With the alternative controls, you aim with the right stick, and mash buttons to perform attacks. <br></li><li><strong>Enjoy gameplay that never gets old:</strong> master the multilayered combat, overcome clever enemies and face epic bosses<br></li><li><strong>Experiment with freestyle combat system:</strong> mix and match combos, switch characters on the fly, and turn enemy abilities against them </li></ul><br><strong>Witness the glory of  beat-em-up 2.0!</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103730/extras/f09256a307f07c83489cc3075f126b53.poster.avif?t=1728991765\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103730/extras/f09256a307f07c83489cc3075f126b53.webm?t=1728991765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103730/extras/f09256a307f07c83489cc3075f126b53.mp4?t=1728991765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Experience the most exciting and immersive beat-em-up combat system ever – become a kickass ninja and slice some demons in style! Join a band of wisecracking warriors in a bloody adventure through the land of mythical monsters and mysterious machines.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Play solo or with friends:</strong> 4 player local and online co-op<br></li><li><strong>Experience immersive and intuitive controls, or use classic \"button mashing\" technique:</strong> right analog stick controls your weapon giving you instant access to extensive moveset. With the alternative controls, you aim with the right stick, and mash buttons to perform attacks. <br></li><li><strong>Enjoy gameplay that never gets old:</strong> master the multilayered combat, overcome clever enemies and face epic bosses<br></li><li><strong>Experiment with freestyle combat system:</strong> mix and match combos, switch characters on the fly, and turn enemy abilities against them </li></ul><br><strong>Witness the glory of  beat-em-up 2.0!</strong>",
